Class MoneyMarket

java.lang.Object
com.banking.cs213project3.Account
com.banking.cs213project3.Savings
com.banking.cs213project3.MoneyMarket
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Account>
public class MoneyMarket extends Savings
MoneyMarket class extends Savings and defines a type of account with monthly interest and fees depending on the loyalty and balance of the customer.
Author:
Michael Kassie Donald Yubeaton
